Uses of Package
org.apache.juneau.json

  • Packages that use org.apache.juneau.json 
    Package Description
    org.apache.juneau.json
    JSON serialization and parsing support
  • Classes in org.apache.juneau.json used by org.apache.juneau.json 
    Class and Description
    JsonParser
    Parses any valid JSON text into a POJO model.
    JsonParserContext
    Configurable properties on the JsonParser class.
    JsonParserSession
    Session object that lives for the duration of a single use of JsonParser.
    JsonSchemaSerializer
    Serializes POJO metadata to HTTP responses as JSON.
    JsonSerializer
    Serializes POJO models to JSON.
    JsonSerializer.Simple
    Default serializer, single quotes, simple mode.
    JsonSerializer.SimpleReadable
    Default serializer, single quotes, simple mode, with whitespace.
    JsonSerializerContext
    Configurable properties on the JsonSerializer class.
    JsonSerializerSession
    Session object that lives for the duration of a single use of JsonSerializer.
    JsonWriter
    Specialized writer for serializing JSON.
